{
  "stem": "15732.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they came up [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and they took over.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After 1 and 1/2 hours somehow of battle.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they took the ship up to Haifa.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were-- I think there were two dead.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think a child was-- died.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there were several of the children were wounded.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Afterwards when they were already masters of the ship, they tried to go around and to give something to drink to those who were injured.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But nobody wanted to look at them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But a interesting thing was the captain, which was a young man, maybe 23 or 24, happened to come in into the hospital place where my father was.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he took a shirt that Shmuelik wore, because he had to change.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he should be one of the-- one of the people, one of the mass, so they wouldn't catch him.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Well, you couldn't believe that he, that young man, is a captain of a ship.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And apparently afterwards, he was really-- gave him a medal in Israel or whatever.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He had afterwards a very big part in building up the Navy, the Israeli Navy.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And when we arrived in Haifa, when we saw Haifa from the far, I will never forget the Hatikvah that was sang then.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was the most tearful, the most screaming Hatikvah that can be.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "All those people after all-- everyone with his bundle of suffering that he went through.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And here you see Palestine and-- and the English are at your back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But we still hoped that they will take us to Cyprus.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "When we have arrived at the shore, we saw that in Haifa, there were no people from the far as one could see.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
